data.title: English Carabao Cup Stats, 2024
data.meta_description: Get the full English Carabao Cup stats for the 2024-25 season on ESPN (UK). Includes leaders in goals, assists, yellow and red cards, and longest winning streaks.
data.text:
Can Matthijs de Ligt revolutionise Man United's defence?

Derek Rae tells the ESPN FC crew what risks Manchester United are taking by singing Matthijs de Ligt from Bayern Munich.

Could Bournemouth sign Barcelona's Julián Araujo?

The Futbol Americas crew are joined by Rodrigo Faez to discuss Barcelona's Julián Araujo potential transfer to Bournemouth.
